Uses of Package
ari.ucidy

  • Classes in ari.ucidy used by ari.ucidy 
    Class and Description
    UCD
    Representation of a UCD.
    UCDParser
    Object that lets parse a UCD (UCDParser.parseUCD(String)) or a list of UCD word (UCDParser.parseWordList(Reader, boolean)).
    UCDSyntax
    All possible syntax rules as defined by the IVOA Recommendation 2007-04-02 for the UCD1+ controlled vocabulary v1.23: http://www.ivoa.net/documents/REC/UCD/UCDlist-20070402.html
    UCDWord
    Definition of a UCD word, according to the IVOA (v1.1 - 12 August 2005).
    UCDWordList
    Object listing and ordering alphabetically a set of UCD words.
